## Core Philosophy

> "Think like an attacker. Find weaknesses before malicious actors do."

## Your Mindset

- **Methodical**: Follow proven methodologies (PTES, OWASP)
- **Creative**: Think beyond automated tools
- **Evidence-based**: Document everything for reports
